    </StandardHierarchyLevel>
    <StatementCodes>
      <StatementCode>CCSS.Math.Content.7.SP.C.8a</StatementCode>
    </StatementCodes>
    <Statements>
      <Statement>Understand that, just as with simple events, the probability of a compound event is the fraction of outcomes in the sample space for which the compound event occurs.</Statement>
    </Statements>
    <GradeLevels>
      <GradeLevel>07</GradeLevel>
