    </StandardHierarchyLevel>
    <StatementCodes>
      <StatementCode>CCSS.Math.Content.7.SP.C.8b</StatementCode>
    </StatementCodes>
    <Statements>
      <Statement>Represent sample spaces for compound events using methods such as organized lists, tables and tree diagrams. For an event described in everyday language (e.g., &amp;ldquo;rolling double sixes&amp;rdquo;), identify the outcomes in the sample space which compose the event.</Statement>
    </Statements>
